original: Melkersson, Gunnar Gustav, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 6/12/05 i Örebro av fabr. Gustaf M. o-. Olga Söderlund. G. 32 m. -tandl. Margareta Harju. Barn: Gumlla f. 35, Erik 38, Lennart 43. — Stud:ex. v. Karoil. lärov. i Örebro 23, tandl :kand. 24, tandl. 27. Prakt, li Aseda 28-29, e. o. tandl. v. Gbgis fcomm. tandpodilvlin. 30-35, ord. 36-42, prakt, i Gbg sed. 43.
translated: Melkersson, Gunnar Gustav, dentist, Gothenburg, b. 12/6/1905 in Örebro to workman Gustaf M. and Olga Söderlund. Married in 1932 to dentist Margareta Harju. Children: Gumlla b. 1935, Erik b. 1938, Lennart b. 1943. - Completed secondary school at Karolinska Gymnasium in Örebro in 1923, dental studies in 1924, dentist certification in 1927. Worked in Aseda from 1928-1929, as temporary dentist at Gothenburg's Municipal Dental Service from 1930-1935, became permanent from 1936-1942, and has been practicing in Gothenburg since 1943.
